title: Live NRL: Manly Sea Eagles v South Sydney Rabbitohs blog, scores, updates | Fox Sports
text:
Maguire: We got it all wrong 1:12 Live NRL: Manly Sea Eagles v South Sydney Rabbitohs blog, scores, updates March 11, 2017 3:45pm by Staff writers Source: FOX SPORTS SOUTH Sydney will be desperate to bounce back from an underwhelming round one loss to Wests Tigers when they head north to Brookvale. 
The Rabbitohs let the young Tigers walk all over them last week and lost captain and fullback Greg Inglis in the process. 
Manly lost to Parramatta in their first outing, and both clubs are searching for a maiden win of 2017.
